p><b>Work-related stress</b></p><p><b>Emotional distress</b></p><p><b>Personal legal and financial issues</b></p><p>Â </p>','Health Care - Heath & Wellness','','publish','open','open','','health-care-heath-wellness','','','2013-06-04 20:51:11','2013-06-04 20:51:11','','0','https://intra-dev.asynchrony.com/help-article/health-care-heath-wellness/','0','help-article','','0');
