INSERT INTO `wp_posts` (`ID`,`post_author`,`post_date`,`post_date_gmt`,`post_content`,`post_title`,`post_excerpt`,`post_status`,`comment_status`,`ping_status`,`post_password`,`post_name`,`to_ping`,`pinged`,`post_modified`,`post_modified_gmt`,`post_content_filtered`,`post_parent`,`guid`,`menu_order`,`post_type`,`post_mime_type`,`comment_count`) VALUES ('202','3','2013-06-05 18:53:50','2013-06-05 18:53:50','<p>Visitors to the Cupples 9 office should park in the garage, a metered spot on the street, or one of 4 visitor parking spaces by the entrance to the surface lot. Only business guests are eligible for parking validation. Personal guests (i.e., friends and family) must pay for parking unless one of the visitor spaces is available.</p>','Cupples 9: Visitor Parking','','publish','open','open','','cupples-9-visitor-parking','','','2013-06-05 19:34:34','2013-06-05 19:34:34','','0','https://intra-dev.asynchrony.com/help-article/visitor-parking-cupples-9/','0','help-article','','0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` (`ID`,`post_author`,`post_date`,`post_date_gmt`,`post_content`,`post_title`,`post_excerpt`,`post_status`,`comment_status`,`ping_status`,`post_password`,`post_name`,`to_ping`,`pinged`,`post_modified`,`post_modified_gmt`,`post_content_filtered`,`post_parent`,`guid`,`menu_order`,`post_type`,`post_mime_type`,`comment_count`) VALUES ('203','3','2013-06-05 18:55:04','2013-06-05 18:55:04','<p>Both the Cupples Garage and the Cupples 9 surface lot are owned by the City of St. Louis, who leases spaces to Cupples 9 tenants. Therefore, both are used for event parking to generate City revenues. On Cardinals weekday home games, depending on the start time, there could be an attendant on duty collecting money when you arrive to work. Just show your access card (Cupples 9 building access card at the surface lot and Cupples Garage access card at the garage) and theyâll let you in at no charge. For weekend games, those who park in the garage can still enter free of charge, but there will be a charge to park in the surface lot. There is also a charge if you leave the surface lot on weekdays and return after 6 pm on the evening of a scheduled home game.</p><h3>Seibert Rd employees</h3><p>Seibert Rd employees who want free parking for evening or weekend Cardinals games can find instructions and necessary documents on the SAFB Asy Community Space (884) on Ace under Manage Project Files/St. Louis Events for Cupples Parking.Â </p>','Cupples 9: Cardinals Parking','','publish','open','open','','cupples-9-cardinals-parking','','','2013-06-12 20:05:06','2013-06-12 20:05:06','','0','https://intra-dev.asynchrony.com/help-article/cardinals-parking-cupples-9/','0','help-article','','0');
