INSERT INTO `wp_posts` (`ID`,`post_author`,`post_date`,`post_date_gmt`,`post_content`,`post_title`,`post_excerpt`,`post_status`,`comment_status`,`ping_status`,`post_password`,`post_name`,`to_ping`,`pinged`,`post_modified`,`post_modified_gmt`,`post_content_filtered`,`post_parent`,`guid`,`menu_order`,`post_type`,`post_mime_type`,`comment_count`) VALUES ('213','3','2013-06-05 19:15:19','2013-06-05 19:15:19','<p>At the Cupples 9 office, there are men\'s and women\'s restrooms on both the 6th &amp; 7th floors. As you exit the elevator on 7, walk past the reception desk, past the bobblehead display and turn left by the kitchen seating area, then veer left again just in front on the kitchen proper. From the 6th floor elevator, veer left, then right down the long hallway, then left at the Forest Park conference room door, then look to your left again for the restroom doors. There are also men\'s and women\'s locker rooms equipped with a shower and a few storage cubbies on the 7th floor. When you exit the elevator, veer left, then left again at the reception desk, then right when you see the elevated white board.</p><p>Locker rooms are also located on the far south side of the tenant lobby on the first floor.</p><p>Â </p>','Cupples 9: Restrooms & Locker Rooms','','publish','open','open','','cupples-9-restrooms-locker-rooms','','','2013-06-12 20:02:36','2013-06-12 20:02:36','','0','https://intra-dev.asynchrony.com/help-article/restrooms-locker-rooms-cupples-9/','0','help-article','','0');
