strong><br /></strong></li><li>Password:Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â <strong>Domain Password</strong></li><li>Connect Server:Â Â Â Â Â <strong>openfire.asynchrony.com</strong></li><li>Resource:Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â <strong>AdiumÂ </strong>(this is fine)</li></ul>','Instant Messaging','','inherit','open','open','','158-revision-3','','','2013-05-31 18:11:37','2013-05-31 18:11:37','','158','https://intra-dev.asynchrony.com/158-revision-3/','0','revision','','0');
