ocket expenses will I incur?</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.myuhcvision.com/members/UnitedHealthcare_memberFAQ.jsp#18\">Is laser vision correction a covered benefit?</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.myuhcvision.com/members/UnitedHealthcare_memberFAQ.jsp#19\">How do I learn more about my benefits?</a></li></ul><h3><strong>Provider Questions</strong></h3><ul type=\"square\"><li><a href=\"https://www.myuhcvision.com/members/UnitedHealthcare_memberFAQ.jsp#20\">Do I need to notify you when I select or if I change my provider?</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.myuhcvision.com/members/UnitedHealthcare_memberFAQ.jsp#21\">How do I obtain a list of in-network vision care providers?</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.myuhcvision.com/members/UnitedHealthcare_memberFAQ.jsp#22\">How do I nominate a vision care provider for inclusion in your network?</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.myuhcvision.com/members/UnitedHealthcare_memberFAQ.jsp#23\">Can I visit a vision care provider outside of the network?</a></li></ul>','Health Care - Vision','','inherit','open','open','','187-revision-2','','','2013-06-04 20:45:19','2013-06-04 20:45:19','','187','https://intra-dev.asynchrony.com/187-revision-2/','0','revision','','0');
