amily out of pocket must be met before eligible claims will be paid in full. Family out of pocket maximum is 3 times the individual out of pocket maximum.</p><p>Once 3 persons covered under the policy meets their out of pocket maximum the family out of pocket maximum is satisfied and eligible claims for any family member will be paid in full.</p><h3><strong>LIFETIME MAXIMUM</strong></h3><p>Network and non-network $5 million combined maximum per covered person.</p>','Health Care - Overview','','inherit','open','open','','184-revision-4','','','2013-06-04 20:45:43','2013-06-04 20:45:43','','184','https://intra-dev.asynchrony.com/184-revision-4/','0','revision','','0');
